OL,3,CJacob Rees-Mogg among Tory MPs whose
OL,4,CGB News programme broke Ofcom's rules
OL,6,FThe watchdog's probe involved five
OL,7,Fepisodes of shows presented separately
OL,8,Fby Sir Jacob Rees-Mogg, Esther McVey,
OL,9,Fand Philip Davies, ITV News' Martha
OL,10,FFairlie reports
OL,12,Fhave been found to have broken Ofcom's
OL,13,Fbroadcasting rules on due impartiality
OL,14,Fduring their GB News programmes.
OL,16,FThe watchdog's probe involved five
OL,17,Fepisodes of shows presented separately
OL,18,Fby former House of Commons leader Sir
OL,19,FJacob Rees-Mogg, minister without
OL,20,Fportfolio Esther McVey, and
OL,21,Fbackbencher Philip Davies.
