OL,3,CJacob Rees-Mogg among Tory MPs whose
OL,4,CGB News programme broke Ofcom's rules
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "Ofcom is obliged
OL,7,Fby law to promote free speech and
OL,8,Fmedia plurality, and to ensure that
OL,9,Falternative voices are heard.
OL,11,F"Its latest decisions, in some cases a
OL,12,Fyear after the programme aired,
OL,13,Fcontravene thoseJduties."
OL,15,FThe media channel added Ofcom has
OL,16,F"arbitrarily changed the test" for
OL,17,Fwhich it holds organisations to
OL,18,Fimpartiality standards.
